docs {
  # Get Ready Tasks
  
  Retrieve all tasks that are ready for execution (no pending dependencies).
  
  ## Response
  - 200: Array of ready tasks
  
  ## Use Case
  This endpoint is useful for identifying which tasks can be started immediately,
  making it ideal for parallel execution planning and task assignment.
}